<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb942a336-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—<ref href="/us/pl/107/273">Pub. L. 107–273</ref> substituted “under this title” for “not more than $1,000”.</p>
